content:
coming from a silent space 

from the edges of the seasons



currently based in tromsø in northern norway

open for collaboration and commissions worldwide



specializing in portrait and landscape photography

but listening attentively to any ideas 

that you find fitting the style and skills



please make contact with any inquiry



.



open booking for portrait photoshooting in tromsø surroundings

with the possibility of private excursion to different locations

make contact for the details, availability and prices
title: karolina nocoń
